	<article class="post-55761 post type-post status-publish hentry category-arctic-poles category-climate-change category-diplomacy category-oceans category-poles category-politics tag-alaska tag-anchorage-alaska tag-arctic-council tag-arctic-ocean tag-arctic-regions tag-canada tag-cold-war-era tag-defense-and-military-forces tag-environment tag-geography tag-glaciers tag-global-warming tag-greenhouse-gas-emissions tag-harding-warren-g tag-ice tag-icebreakers tag-juneau-alaska tag-kenai-peninsula-alaska tag-law-of-the-sea-un-convention tag-moscow-russia tag-north-pole tag-obama-barack tag-oceans-and-seas tag-offshore-drilling-and-exploration tag-oil-petroleum-and-gasoline tag-republican-party tag-rogozin-dmitri-o tag-russia tag-ships-and-shipping tag-state-department tag-united-states-international-relations tag-young-don per-harding-warren-g per-obama-barack per-rogozin-dmitri-o per-young-don des-cold-war-era des-defense-and-military-forces des-environment des-geography des-glaciers des-global-warming des-greenhouse-gas-emissions des-ice des-icebreakers des-law-of-the-sea-un-convention des-oceans-and-seas des-offshore-drilling-and-exploration des-oil-petroleum-and-gasoline des-ships-and-shipping des-united-states-international-relations org-arctic-council org-republican-party org-state-department geo-alaska geo-anchorage-alaska geo-arctic-ocean geo-arctic-regions geo-canada geo-juneau-alaska geo-kenai-peninsula-alaska geo-moscow-russia geo-north-pole geo-russia" id="post-55761">
